{"tid":1073541,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"其實舊時既兒歌都幾好聽。","createTime":"2019-03-22T18:02:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-23T09:50:47.000Z","uid":112644,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"3ce3ec54ab54db576feab3f66b68e120b515ed75","tid":1073541,"uid":112644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T18:02:19.000Z","msg":"聽得多左而家既流行曲<br />\n發現其實好多以前既兒歌反而仲有味道<br />\n好多都未必有人識<br />\n但係旋律幾好聽 幾懷念<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家仲有無貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/tOkX3kihmXc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FtOkX3kihmXc&d=WP5iSE3nEMa4dMETfl%2FD18emYpZY8oJkMX6FO%2BQoeBQ%3D&h=873d7a8f\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/tOkX3kihmXc</a>"},{"pid":"0c888b5df72a6a86d94285ce6c0f697b55fc80c6","tid":1073541,"uid":216004,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T18:08:26.000Z","msg":"生命有價"},{"pid":"e83c3b742eb59b3f892b2affcedef4670c8a01fa","tid":1073541,"uid":141901,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T18:31:49.000Z","msg":"夜靜望晚星<br />\n擦擦我眼睛<br />\n蟋蟀烏鴉都給我靜聽<br />\n聽見風與樹和聲恬靜<br />\n祈求明日放晴<br />\n<br />\n遇著遇見他<br />\n跌碰也有他<br />\n伸出一雙手幫我未怕<br />\n我與好友道盡心裡話<br />\n看到晚星降下<br />\n<br />\n望著望著有千億個夢兒<br />\n浮浮沉沉夜空金色光線<br />\n嗚啦啦...嗚啦啦...<br />\n浮沉雲霧有時<br />\n<br />\n實現實現我心千個夢兒<br />\n仍然常期待星星的加冕<br />\n嗚啦啦...嗚啦啦啦...<br />\n世界也會在意<br />\n<br />\n嗚啦...嗚啦啦啦...<br />\n嗚啦...嗚啦啦啦...<br />\n嗚啦...嗚啦啦啦...<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fd278959cfee3b3248fd3848e32c5ea3ef6d2f1","tid":1073541,"uid":146435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T20:22:20.000Z","msg":"是龜也是頭 是龜頭也是賓周<br />\n十二隻恐龍去野餐"},{"pid":"28c8eb93ab02e7510a5f77c952f83f75c6367b01","tid":1073541,"uid":29702,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T21:08:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0cb8eee442b0458e69604a